text: I really admire your efforts in getting a perfect 10 pointer throughout. Kaafi dedication aur hardwork lagta hai and hats off to you for doing that. Keep moving with the same spirit. Milke kabhi TA mentor ki bitching karenge üòÇ

text: Tere jitna dance enthusiasm aur kisi me nahi dekha bro. Tera enthu dekhke inspiration milti thi ki kuch karo to itni dedication aur commitment se karo. Hats off to you bro!

text: Mishra ji yaad hai first year me jab mai apke upar swimming karta tha mime me? Wo alag hi time tha. Kitne maze kiye the mime practice me.

text: Saath me football aur badminton khelne me bahut aaya. Wing me to itne maze kiye hi saath me sabne. Keep up with your amazing sporting skills and talent. Cheers!

text: First sem me lagne laga tha ki ESC101 instructor tu hi hai, sab kuch to tere se hi samajhte the üòÇ. Game bhi ekdum mast banaya tha advanced track wala. Endless bulla sessions, OAT parties and group me milke ek dusre ki khichai karna hamesha yaad rahega.
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text:
Yo,
I found you to be quite sensible, understanding and a kind person. Sense of humour pe comment nahi karunga :P. Yash ki T-shirts steal karne me maza aata tha na kitna xD. Keep being the good human being that you are and all the best for your future!
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text: Kaafi chill person. Mostly to mess me hi baat hui hum logon ki par kaafi sahi tha utna bhi. Ab aakhirkaar unhi discussions ki vajeh se tu course topper ban paaya :P Enjoy karo aur aese hi chaapte raho
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text: Acads ka first night out saath me hi tha library me. Remember the "aur kaisi ho?" incident? That was really fun xD. Future me milke firse treat plan karte hain ab :P All the best ü§ó
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text:
Kaafi dedicated and hardworking person. Jab dekho code hi karta rehta h :P
It was great living in the same wing, parallel ke assignment ke time to maza hi aa jaata tha. Will not forget you and Devansh teaming up on research and making fun of me. Had a lot of fun in the last 1.5 months. 
MIT me jake bhul mat jaana. 10 saal baad vapis ayenge :P
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text:
Yo Ayush,
Exactly yaad nahi but I suppose Yash ke through hi mile honge, and it's been a pleasure to have interacted with you since. Chahe wo tere room ki unique decoration dekhna ho, US ke failed reunion plans hon ya mess me Hemant ke maze. Stay the sensible, kind and chaapu person that you are and make sure to remember us fellas
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text: Ballu bro, teri dedication and enthusiasm for work hamesha se inspiring rahi hai. Shuru se hi itna aage ki planning kar leta tha, jahan ka mujhe idea bhi nahi tha. Usse motivation milta tha ki mai bhi chizen explore karun, information acquire karun. Baki sense of humour ka to kya hi kehna (achha nahi hai xD). Aage bhi chaapte raho aur ham logon ko inspire karte raho.
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text: Bro, tere jitna enthusiasm football ke liye kisi me nahi dekha. Kabhi bhi bula lo khelne ke liye aur bina second thoughts ke aa jaata tha. Inspiration milti thi ki kuch karo to itni dedication se karo. Keep up with it.
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text:
Chaapu boy!!
Mostly games and sports me hi interaction hua. Pehle football me aur fir end me CBG me. Maza hi aa gya tha uss din CBG room me to harane me (because religion wale board se decide hona tha na :P). Aese hi chaapte raho aur khelte raho.

text:
My academic mentor for all common courses ü§ó
SG time se shuru hui aur ab tak friendship vaise hi kayam hai

Cheers to our friendship! Hope to stay in touch. Good luck for your future

text: Library se aa raha hai? Ye mera fixed question ban gaya tha xD. Saath me gurudware jaane me kaafi sahi lagta tha. Aese hi cool chaapu bane raho

text: You are what a person should be, good natured, kind and helpful. Stay the same aur kabhi to chocolates dedo üò≠üòõ. Anyways, all the best for the next year. Keep spamming üòÇ

text: Aakhiri kuch din wing me aur cricket ground pe kuch maze kiye. Last night terrace pe kitna sahi tha. Dosa incident ke baad wing me adopt to kar hi liya, ab mai bhi chalunga next wing trip pe

text:
Yo Hemant,
All our interactions in mess and wing were really fun. The way you defend your claims, and attempt to make others laugh is commendable. Keep shining!

text: Saath me projects karne me kaafi maza aaya. Bas ye nahi pata ki hum dono ki vajeh se chale wo ya SRD ka jadoo tha (ya umbrella org ka) xD. Aese hi deep learning models train karte raho aur chaapte raho

text:
Bahut decent and kind. Kabhi bhi milna ho to RM/KD pahunch jaata tha. Vahan na ho to doubt hota tha ki aaj yahan kaise nahi :P
Convince karke tujhe inter IIT le gye aur vahan lol ho gya hamare saath üòÇ Par maza bahut aaya tha.
Really nice getting to know you :)

text:
Roomie bhai,
kahan to bahut hi seedhe sharif lage the pehle din, jaise hi shayariyan shuru hui sab palat gya üòÇ. Maze to bahut kiye first year me saath me - antaragni me sumo fight, hec campaigning lol, pratyush ke saath tripling, badminton and many more. Apna talent aese hi barkarar rakho, bas audience dekhke üòÇ
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text:
Yo bro,
Same JEE batch, same college, same hall, same home city. Sab same hi hai shuru se. Aage bhi batate rehna kahin apply kare to, mai bhi kar dunga xD. Milte hain jald hi. Cheers!
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text: Bhai mile to aesa mile. Ek time pe to apna introduction ho gya tha - Manish ka bhai! 4 saal me kitna kuch kiya yaar. Mera saubhagya hai ki first year summers me same room share kiya. Aese hi chaapte raho aur hamari family ka naam roshan karte raho
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text: One of the most dedicated and work oriented person I met in iitk. Sorry agar hum log kabhi cope up nahi kar payen ho apke level and pace se. Jaldi se umbrella organization banao aur ham sabko hire karo usme xD. Jokes apart, keep working and shining like this. Cheers!

text: Tere bare me to uss din mess me bata hi diya tha jo tha :P. Jokes apart, assignments/projects me cool rehna koi tere se seekhe, Rarely hi stress me dekha hoga tujhe. Defending to achhi karta hi hai football me. That game in CBG was really fun (mai jeeta tha because religion wala main tha :P)
author: Shobhit  Jagga

text:
Yo bro,
ENG saath me kiya tha vahan se teri dedication aur work ethics dikh gye the. Unse kaafi inspiration mila. Aese hi chaapte raho. All the best! ü§ó

text: Tripling karni hai? Badminton khelna hai? Wolf of wall street dekhni hai? Ya aaj bhi gf se video call hi karte rehna hai? :P. Bahut maze kiye yaar first year wale room me. Comedy to achhi karta hi hai, wo ek dhobi wala joke mujhe aaj tak yaad hai. Aese hi cool bane raho aur management karte raho mere se manifesto banwa keüòÇ

text:

text: Unfortunately tu mujhe tabhi yaad karta tha jab midsem ya endsem aane wale hote the. Fir tune realize kar liya ki kisi aur se puchhna better hoga tab to exams me bhi yaad karna chhod diya üò©. Jokes apart, maze kitne saath me, wing me. Ab jaldi se milte hain aur badminton khelte hain ü§ó

text: A really chaapu person! Next phase of life ke liye all the best. Practice kar lena sahi se, agli baar hara dunga badminton me

text: Kisi din saath me squash khelna hai bro. Haar jaunga par tu bhi to out of touch hai ab üòõ. Ye alag baat hai ki uske baad moov bhi tere se hi lunga jab sprain aa jayega lol. Hamne to biotechnology me bata bhi diya tha covid ka rahasya, inn logon se ab tak solve nahi hua ü§£. Aese hi apni sporting spirit continued rakho aur lab me bhi naam roshan karo ü§ó

text: Bahut hi zyaaada chill hai. Matlab kaafi surprise hota tha ki itna relaxed aur tension free koi kaise ho sakta hai. Spte sore exam hi miss kar diya tha ek baar. Ek baar first row me so raha tha RM101 me, mujhe uthana pada tha mid class me üòÇ. Aese hi life enjoy karte raho

text: Architecture me kitna discussion karte the har lecture ke baad. Misunderstanding ki vajeh se same group nahi hua uska bahut bura laga. Same group hota to dono ke liye kitna easy ho jaata. Wing me to maze kiye hi, especially last month me. Aese hi high hoke meetings attend karte raho üòÇ

text: Asati bro, tere se baat karke achha hi lagta tha hamesha (unless gaming related baat ho). Aese hi sensible aur mature bane raho. ELS me meri badaulat team haari hai hamesha lol. "fraud" guess karane wala epic tha aur hamesha yaad rahega. Itni sharp memory kahan se laate ho yaar üòÇ

text:

text:
Bhai - bhai!
Shuru se end tak close neighbours rahe aur padhai fun sab saath me kiya. RM wale friend se saath bhi kitna maza kiya courses me. Will always be inspired by your positively, health consciousness and dedication towards work.
Cheers!

text:
Yo Yugesh,
I have been grateful ki second year me long walks pe jake tune mere me kuch wisdom daal di. Antaragni me itni treats le lene ke liye sorry (genuinely!). You are a wonderful orator and an amazingly social person. Keep it up and all the best for your Swiss life ahead! Bhulne ka to option nahi hi hai
